  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Sales Manager",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>We are looking for an experienced and results-driven Sales Manager to lead and grow our beauty sales operations. This role focuses on driving revenue, managing client relationships and supporting the team to achieve consistent performance.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Lead and motivate the sales team to consistently achieve monthly and yearly sales targets, driving measurable revenue growth</li><li>Develop and implement effective sales strategies to increase sales of beauty services and products</li><li>Build and maintain strong, long-term relationships with clients and business partners to enhance customer loyalty and business opportunities</li><li>Identify and pursue new sales opportunities to expand the customer base and market presence</li><li>Manage the full sales process from initial consultation through to closing, ensuring customer satisfaction and sales effectiveness</li><li>Monitor sales performance metrics and prepare detailed reports and forecasts to inform strategic decisions</li><li>Coach, train, and support sales team members to enhance their sales techniques and customer service skills, improving overall team performance</li><li>Collaborate closely with internal teams to ensure seamless operations and an exceptional customer experience</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Proven experience as a Sales Manager or senior sales role</li><li>Experience in beauty, aesthetics, wellness or related fields is an advantage</li><li>Strong leadership, communication and negotiation skills</li><li>Target-driven with strong customer and service mindset</li><li>Able to manage multiple priorities in a fast-paced environment</li><li>Self-motivated and results-oriented</li></ul><p></p>",
